org.keycloak.protocol

Class RestartLoginCookie

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.keycloak.protocol.RestartLoginCookie

  • public class RestartLoginCookie
extends Object
    This is an an encoded token that is stored as a cookie so that if there is a client timeout, then the client session can be restarted.
